Tea tree?) made us feel so comfortable. Then come the samples (unless of course that's not allowed and Lauren was just super cool in which case that didnt happen) I put some lotion on my shoulders and we ate some dried, infused bananas. I currently feel soothed, not to any extreme degree, but in a pleasant, enjoyable way. All in all, I recommend Muz Muz if not just for it's pleasant products, but for its exceptional atmosphere.
